title: cannot label data
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

When I activate DEEPLABCUT GUI, I can execute extract frames command and make some images in 'labeled-data' folder. However, I can't label frames. 

### Operating System

Windows 11

### DeepLabCut version

2.2.0.6

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

cpu

### Steps To Reproduce

_No response_
